    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b You've gotta see this beauty in person\u2014it's absolutely spotless and honestly looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I've taken incredible care of it, and it drives like an absolute dream. If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s been loved and kept in pristine shape, this is the one for you. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 44500.0,
