    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is a museum-grade 2004 Porsche 911 Carrera 4S, featuring the iconic wide-body silhouette and integrated rear reflector strip. This specimen is powered by a 3.6L naturally aspirated flat-six, delivering 315 hp through a tactile 6-speed manual transaxle. The mechanical integrity is paramount: the IMS bearing has been proactively replaced with a LN Engineering ceramic solution, and the cooling system has been overhauled with a low-temp thermostat and metal-impeller water pump. The chassis remains taut, benefiting from factory-spec Bilstein dampers and refreshed bushings, ensuring razor-sharp turn-in and neutral handling characteristics. The paint depth is consistent across all panels, and the interior is devoid of bolster wear or soft-touch plastic degradation. A true analog masterpiece for the discerning collector seeking mechanical perfection.",
